cu.explanation_en: Setting remote SCTP address to an unreachable IP causes wrong routing, preventing F1 interface connection to DU and causing setup failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting Ta4 timing parameter to 0 causes timing misalignment in front-haul configuration, leading to synchronization issues and data transmission failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Ta4 定時參數設定為 0 會導致前傳配置中的定時錯位，造成同步問題和數據傳輸失敗。
